  * The "new stable version 1.6" release hit the street!
  * Adjusted VCS-* fields in debian/control for stable.
  * Adjust STABLE_VERSION + NEXT_VERSION calculation in debian/rules for
    stable.
  * Adjust debian/watch for stable.
